OL,3,CNew Zealand would support removal of
OL,4,CAndrew from line of succession
OL,6,FIn his letter to Prime Minister Sir
OL,7,FKeir, Anthony Albanese said Andrew was
OL,8,Ffacing "grave allegations", adding:
OL,9,F"Australians take them seriously."
OL,11,FDespite being stripped of his title
OL,12,Flast year, the former duke of York is
OL,13,Fstill eighth in line to the throne,
OL,14,Fand an Act of Parliament would be
OL,15,Frequired to remove Andrew and prevent
OL,16,Fhim from ever becoming king.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@ZO]qD@AOUqD@bO]
