OL,3,CNew Zealand would support removal of
OL,4,CAndrew from line of succession
OL,6,FThe UK Government will consider
OL,7,Fintroducing such legislation once
OL,8,Fpolice have finished their
OL,9,Finvestigation into the King's
OL,10,Fdisgraced brother, the Press
OL,11,FAssociation understands.
OL,13,FMeanwhile, on Tuesday, the Liberal
OL,14,FDemocrats will seek to force the
OL,15,Fpublic release of files relating to
OL,16,FAndrew Mountbatten-Windsor's
OL,17,Fappointment as a trade envoy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
