OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1771938194
OL,3,CNew Zealand would support removal of
OL,4,CAndrew from line of succession
OL,6,FThe Lib Dems will table a humble
OL,7,Faddress in the Commons ` the same
OL,8,Farcane mechanism the Tories used to
OL,9,Fpress for the release of files on Lord
OL,10,FMandelson's appointment as ambassador
OL,11,F` in a bid to compel the Government to
OL,12,Fdisclose information about Andrew, who
OL,13,Fserved as a trade envoy between 2001
OL,14,Fand 2011.
OL,16,FThe motion will call for the release
OL,17,Fof papers relating to Andrew's
OL,18,Fappointment to the post, including any
OL,19,Fvetting and any correspondence from
OL,20,FLord Mandelson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
