OL,3,CNew Zealand would support removal of
OL,4,CAndrew from line of succession
OL,6,FLib Dem leader Sir Ed Davey said: "The
OL,7,Fpublic is rightly demanding to know
OL,8,Fhow Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor was
OL,9,Fappointed to represent our nation in a
OL,10,Fhigh-level trade role.
OL,12,F"The Liberal Democrats are moving a
OL,13,Fbinding motion to force the Government
OL,14,Fto come clean.
OL,16,F"We need to see the vetting files, the
OL,17,Fdue diligence reports, and the
OL,18,Fcorrespondence to understand how this
OL,19,Fappointment came to be, and whether
OL,20,Fglaring warning signs were missed.
OL,26,@nD@cOUtD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
